Rich Jaroslovsky , editor at large 
and technology columnist at Bloomberg News, discusses his 
"Surface," which is the a new windows-powered tablet computer 
made by Microsoft. Jaroslovsky talked to Kathleen Hays and 
Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on June 
19, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:22
 